<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_253_r2l22"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> hanns als wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> nehſt <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_253_r2l23">von der gült <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> . dıe Jr vns auf ſand michelſtag <expan>nehſtu<ex>er</ex>gangen</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_253_r2l24"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>fallen</expan> vnd noch ſchuldıg ſeyt / daʒ vns niht füklıch <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> / dıe <expan>leng<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_253_r2l25">ʒu ſteen <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu ıſt vns ſeıther . des noch kein <expan>auſrıchtıgu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_253_r2l26">eẅch <expan>geſcheh<ex>en</ex></expan> . <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅch <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> . Jr gedenkt / daʒ wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_253_r2l27">der gült <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒogenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> becʒalt <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> . VVan geſcheͣch des niht . ſo </ab>
